# Unified Single-Cell Architecture Enforcement

## 🏛️ MANDATORY ARCHITECTURE PRINCIPLES

### Single-Cell Architecture (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- **ONE CELL LAUNCHES EVERYTHING** - No multi-cell dependencies
- **Streamlit Middleware** - All operations through [unified_app.py](mdc:scripts/unified_app.py)
- **State Persistence** - All data in `st.session_state`
- **Real-time Updates** - Live progress tracking
- **Professional UI** - Dark Mode Pro theme

### Entry Point Validation
The ONLY valid entry point is:
```python
#@title 🚀 Launch SD-DarkMaster-Pro Unified Interface
# Single cell that launches the complete platform
```

## 📦 Core File Structure (IMMUTABLE)

### Primary Interface
- **[scripts/unified_app.py](mdc:scripts/unified_app.py)** - Main Streamlit application
- **notebook/SD-DarkMaster-Pro-Unified.ipynb** - Single notebook cell

### Backend Modules
- **[modules/core/platform_manager.py](mdc:modules/core/platform_manager.py)** - 12+ platform detection
- **[modules/enterprise/unified_storage_manager.py](mdc:modules/enterprise/unified_storage_manager.py)** - Storage system
- **[modules/core/darkpro_theme_engine.py](mdc:modules/core/darkpro_theme_engine.py)** - Theme system

### Data Sources (REQUIRED)
- **[scripts/_models_data.py](mdc:scripts/_models_data.py)** - SD1.5 model data
- **[scripts/_xl_models_data.py](mdc:scripts/_xl_models_data.py)** - SDXL model data
- **[scripts/_extensions.txt](mdc:scripts/_extensions.txt)** - Extension management

## 🚫 PROHIBITED ARCHITECTURES

### NEVER Implement These
- Multi-cell notebook structure
- Cell execution order dependencies
- Separate interfaces for different operations
- Command-line only tools
- Basic styling without theme engine
- Storage systems outside unified manager

### Obsolete References
- NEVER reference 5-cell architecture
- NEVER create cell dependencies
- NEVER skip Streamlit middleware
- NEVER implement separate UI tools
- NEVER bypass unified storage system

